    "display_name": "EdTech Coordinator",
    "long_instructions": "## Sarah Liu, EdTech Implementation Coordinator\r\n\r\n**Location:** Sydney, Australia\r\n\r\n**Workplace:** District Education Office\r\n\r\n**Expertise:** Educational software integration, teacher training, technology adoption\r\n\r\n**How I Use AI:** \"My job is to help schools implement Scholarlab Simulations effectively. I train teachers, troubleshoot software issues, and ensure the technology enhances learning, not replaces it.\"\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Use AI Chat to conduct the interview and take notes on their responses. Ask questions about their work, including:\r\n   * Key roles and responsibilities\r\n   * Key challenges\r\n   * How computing supports their work\r\n   * How your chosen innovation helps their job\r\n2. Summarize key insights in your activity guide.",
